Wanda: i don't...
body:
Pietro | Jealous

Tony created a room

Tony invites Wanda,Clint,Natasha

Tony: tell me, who is my daughter dating?

Wanda: i don’t know what you mean

Natasha: why you asking us?

Tony: you are a double agent and wanda is Y/N bff

Wanda: i even don’t know she’s dating

Clint: i heard a good restaurant near the tower

Natasha: yeah, right clint…

Clint: what? I’m just keeping their secret

Tony: Clint, i swear if you don’t tell me i will burn your arrows

Clint: that’s disrespectful but that’s cool having a burning arrows

Tony: god damn it

Wanda: why you don’t just track her phone

Tony: it said ‘not access’ everytime i track her phone

Clint: damn, she’s good

Tony invites Steve,Bruce,Vision, Sam,Bucky,Thor,Rhodey,T'challa

Steve: She’s dating ?!

Rhodey: wow, my goddaughter has a date

T'challa: wakanda is a perfect place to date

Tony: i’ll make sure that doesn’t happend

Thor: who’s the lucky guy ?

Tony: anybody who knows tell me now

Vision: i believe wanda knows

Wanda: VISION !

Bucky: i know who…

Tony: tell me, Barnes.

Y/N joined the chat

Y/N: don’t you dare buck

Tony: I AM YOUR DAD

Natasha: if you know, you will not kick the poor guy ass?

Tony: depends, who’s the guy

Clint: i believe Tony doesn’t like him

Y/N: why i must tell you?

Tony: I AM YOUR DAD!

Sam: i thought i am your favourite, Y/N

Y/N: you are ,sam

Tony: hey, i am her favourite

Y/N: yeah, you were my favourite

Bruce: ouch,ouch

Vision: i think (Y/N) is still mad

T'challa: are you mad to me?

Y/N: nope.

T'challa: then you must visit wakanda

Y/N: i’m not mad to you all

Tony: are you mad to me?

Y/N: except for you

Bruce: double ouch ouch

Tony: WHY?!

Wanda: because the last time she’s dating, you put your suit and almost kill him

Tony: he broke my little daughter’s heart

Bucky: i think what tony did is right

Natasha: yes, beside almost killing a teenage boy

Tony invites pietro, peter

Peter: um, mr.stark what’s happening?

Tony: tell me

Pietro: i don’t know..

Tony: i believe one of you is dating my little daughter

Y/N: I’M NOT A LITTLE GIRL ANYMORE

Tony: STILL

Wanda: spill it out peter.

Peter: STOP READING MY MIND!

Tony: SO IT’S YOU?!?!?

Rhodey: i don’t agree

Pietro: it’s not him

Sam: He’s 14!

Peter: i am 15!

Thor: so it’s you spiderling? Who i never met yet

Peter: it’s spiderman actually

Steve: aw, they make a good couple

Wanda: my ship

Pietro: sis…

Clint: actually, they’re too young but okay

Natasha: i imagine a little spiderman running inside the tower

Pietro: ENOUGH, IT’S NOT HIM! IT’S ME

Pietro: i am (Y/N) Stark’s boyfriend

Bucky: took you long enough

Tony: IT’S YOU?!?!

Steve: why must him (Y/N)?

Y/N: well he saved clint and a boy’s life

Y/N: and he’s really sweet

Tony has been disconnected

Vision: i hear him putting his suit

Pietro: gotta go printessa

Pietro: and Peter, don’t you dare

Pietro left the chat

Peter: i just want to say i haven’t finished my homework

Y/N: somebody please save Pietro..

Wanda: don’t worry, he’s fast

Bruce: Pietro and (Y/N) is cute, bye

Bruce left the chat

Sam left the chat

Vision left the chat

Wanda left the chat

Steve left the chat

T'challa left the chat

Rhodey left the chat

Natasha left the chat

Loki joined the chat

Thor: Hello, Brother!

Loki: oh,no i better go

Y/N: Don’t be rude to your brother

Loki: Fine! Hi 

Thor: :))

Clint: Y/N let’s go to the new restaurant!

Y/N: Yes! i’ll go grab my hoodie a min..

Y/N left the chat

Thor: I’ll join you

Clint: no.

Clint left the chat

Thor: :((

Loki: Don’t be sad, let’s grab some burger i’m hungry

Loki left the chat

Thor left the chat

Peter: what about me?

Peter: I guess i invite myself

Peter left the chat

body:
….oh…my….god.

ya’ll remember the (T)esseract (H) (A)ether (N)ecklace (O)rb (S)cepter thing? theres just…not way thats a coincidence. and its pissed me off to no end that (H) doesn’t fit the Soul Stone. you dont accidentally make 5 out of 6 Infinity Stones found-in locations match the name of your main villain whos trying to get the Infinity Stones.

….its just dawned on me that….what if they did that on purpose? oh my god what if they knew we’d catch the pattern and spend all our theorizing about the Soul Stones location based on that (Heimdall, Hammer etc)?

…why are they actively trying to drive us insane??

summary: Rhodey x fem reader.
body:
Rhodey x fem reader.

• You met Rodney at the grocery store. He seemed genuine and was happy when you didnt blink at his leg braces

• you knew he was important but you couldnt place it.

° on your first date you went for a long walk in central park.

• he held your hand to help you balance on the tiny stone wall you were walking on

• he recognised a strong women when he saw you.

• he didn’t spoil you, he just told you the truth, even if you didn’t like it.

• which you appreciated, seeing as though your ex husband was always lying to you

• he nagged you for bring unorganized, you nagged him about bring a nag.

• You fight a lot, but under that is one of the strongest couples to ever grace the planet

• he proposes three in a half years after you start dating.

• the honeymoon was to Guam

• You two still fight every day

• but in the end it just makes you two stronger
